e%20para%20el%20coronavirus%20en%20India%202.4%20Mas%20informaci\u00f3n%20Coronavirus%20en%20India%20La%20India%20fue%20uno%20de%20los%20primeros%20pa\u00edses%20en%20implementar%20una%20prohibici\u00f3n%20de%20entrada%20al%20turismo;%20debido%20a%20la%20expansi\u00f3n%20La%20India%20fue%20uno%20de%20los%20primeros%20pa\u00edses%20en%20implementar%20una%20prohibici\u00f3n%20de%20entrada%20al%20turismo;%20debido%20a%20la%20expansi\u00f3n%20del%20coronavirus%20(Covid-19)%20en%20su%20territorio.%20Esta%20prohibici\u00f3n%20de%20entrada%20se%20ha%20retirado%20en%20octubre%202021%20y%20ya%20se%20vuelven%20a%20emitir%20visados.%20Revise%20nuestra%20web%20o%20nuestro%20Facebook%20para%20mantenerse%20informado%20sobre%20la%20situaci\u00f3n%20actual%20del%20coronavirus%20en%20la%20India.%20Situaci\u00f3n%20del%20Coronavirus%20en%20la%20India%20Los%20positivos%20en%20Covid-19%20se%20han%20reducido%20enormemente%20durante%20el%202022%20como%20en%20todas%20partes%20y%20la%20situaci\u00f3n%20est\u00e1%20normalizada.%20Oficialmente%20sigue%20siendo%20necesario%20el%20uso%20de%20mascarilla%20en%20muchos%20lugares%20pero%20muy%20pocas%20personas%20lo%20cumplen.%20Viajar%20a%20la%20India%20en%20tiempos%20de%20Covid-19%20El%20Gobierno%20de%20la%20India%20ha%20anunciado%20en%20octubre%20de%202021%20la%20vuelta%20de%20los%20viajes%20tur\u00edsticos%20a%20la%20India.%20Regreso%20de%20los%20viajes%20a%20la%20India%20El%20turismo%20nacional%20lleva%20muchos%20meses%20funcionando%20normalmente.%20Los%20trenes,%20el%20metro,%20los%20vuelos%20nacionales,%20los%20mercados%20y%20los%20restaurantes%20tambi\u00e9n%20pueden%20funcionar%20normalmente%20y%20el%20Taj%20Mahal%20reabri\u00f3%20sus%20puertas.%20Requisitos%20para%20viajar%20a%20la%20India%20covid%202023%20Para%20viajar%20a%20la%20India%20es%20necesario%20tener%20la%20vacuna%20(pauta%20completa,%202%20dosis%20normalmente)%20o%20realizar%20un%20test%20PCR.%20Ya%20no%20es%20necesario%20rellenar%20el%20formulario%20de%20llegada.%20Seguro%20de%20cancelaci\u00f3n%20y%20de%20viaje%20para%20el%20coronavirus%20en%20India%20En%20el%20momento%20en%20el%20que%20se%20puede%20volver%20a%20viajar%20a%20la%20India%20recomendamos%20a%20nuestros%20clientes%20el%20viajar%20con%20seguro%20de%20viaje,%20ya%20que%20en%20estos%20momentos%20es%20a\u00fan%20m\u00e1s%20importante.%20Por%20este%20motivo,%20la%20India%20Incre\u00edble%20ha%20alcanzado%20un%20acuerdo%20con%20Seguros%20IATI%20por%20el%20que%20nuestros%20clientes%20y%20lectores%20tendr\u00edan%20un%205%%20de%20descuento%20sobre%20los%20ya%20de%20por%20si%20buenos%20precios%20que%20ofrecen%20a%20los%20viajeros%20para%20su%20seguro%20de%20viaje%20para%20la%20India.%20Cubren%20diversas%20incidencias%20que%20se%20puedan%20producir%20debido%20al%20coronavirus,%20la%20m\u00e1s%20importante%20el%20no%20poder%20realizar%20el%20viaje%20por%20dar%20positivo.%20Para%20echar%20un%20vistazo%20a%20sus%20p\u00f3lizas%20hay%20que%20hacer%20click%20en%20la%20imagen%20o%20usar%20el%20link%20y%20podremos%20ver%20las%20distintas%20opciones%20para%20nuestro%20viaje%20con%20el%20correspondiente%20descuento.%20Enlace:%20http://www.iatiseguros.com/?r=3756592944019%20Mas%20informaci\u00f3n%20S\u00edganos%20en%20Facebook%20para%20la%20informaci\u00f3n%20para%20viajar%20a%20la%20India%20por%20la%20pandemia%20del%20Covid-19:\u00a0https://www.facebook.com/laindiaincreible/%20\u2013\u00a0P\u00e1gina%20del%20Ministerio%20de%20salud%20de%20la%20India\u2013\u00a0Gobierno%20de%20Espa\u00f1a\u00a0\u2013\u00a0Organizaci\u00f3n%20Mundial%20de%20la%20Salud%20Tambi\u00e9n%20tenemos%20informaci\u00f3n%20actualizada%20sobre%20el%20Coronavirus%20en%20Nepal,\u00a0Coronavirus%20en%20Sri%20Lanka%20y%20Coronavirus%20en%20Maldivas.nhttps://laindiaincreible.com/coronavirus-en-india/", "http://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?url=https://laindiaincreible.com/coronavirus-en-india/&title=Coronavirus%20en%20India.%20Requisitos%20viaje%202023", "https://laindiaincreible.com/visado-india-online-e-visa-para-india/", "